data.description: This particular corner unit is set back, with a scenic view just across the street from the main park and pool. This fabulous home has a large outdoor patio to enjoy the south Florida weather, it's  surrounded by privacy fence. Inside you'll find a spacious living room with wood like flooring, kitchen with  stainless appliances, a glass washer & eat-in bar and dining room area.  It also has a central vac system in the home. There are 2 SGD on the 1st floor leading to the courtyard. Upstairs there is a balcony in each bedroom . The 2nd floor consists of 2 spacious master suites each with private bathroom. The  master bath features a remodeled step in shower and dual sinks with a  granite top.
